      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so much easier to think about it being over. like, if i could just stop the clock, the constant weight of this would just stop. it's not even that i want to hurt, i just want the emptiness to end. it feels like the only logical way to get peace is for everything to just... stop. do you think it's wrong to want that kind of peace?",
